flowchart TD
    Prompt[User prompt arrives] --> Detect{Auto-detection rules<br/>match content?}

    Detect -- "pasted transcript" --> AutoDebrief[auto-detection.md<br/>fires q-debrief workflow]
    Detect -- "social post screenshot" --> AutoEngage[auto-detection.md<br/>fires q-engage]
    Detect -- "comment on someone's content" --> SocialGate[social-reaction-gate.md<br/>extract poster's claims first]
    Detect -- "drafting external content" --> VoiceRule[voice-enforcement.md<br/>apply founder-voice skill]
    Detect -- "design work" --> DesignAuto[design-auto-invoke.md<br/>load kipi-design skills]
    Detect -- "AUDHD-relevant output" --> AUDHD[audhd-interaction.md<br/>apply executive function rules]
    Detect -- "none" --> Direct[Default path]

    AutoDebrief --> Apply
    AutoEngage --> Apply
    SocialGate --> Apply
    VoiceRule --> Apply
    DesignAuto --> Apply
    AUDHD --> Apply
    Direct --> Apply

    Apply[Model generates response with<br/>active rules in context] --> Edit{Touching files?}
    Edit -- yes --> Wiring[wiring-check.md<br/>verify connections]
    Edit -- yes --> MDHygiene[md-hygiene.md<br/>line budgets, section pinning]
    Edit -- yes --> FolderStruct[folder-structure.md<br/>placement enforced]
    Edit -- no --> Done[Response delivered]
    Wiring --> Done
    MDHygiene --> Done
    FolderStruct --> Done

    classDef detect fill:#fef3c7,stroke:#92400e
    classDef rule fill:#dbeafe,stroke:#1e40af
    classDef gate fill:#fce7f3,stroke:#9d174d
    class Detect,Edit detect
    class AutoDebrief,AutoEngage,SocialGate,VoiceRule,DesignAuto,AUDHD,Wiring,MDHygiene,FolderStruct rule
